            <p class="handbook-content-1 mt-4">In recent years, Korea has become a famous tourist destination around the world. This place has a temperate climate with four distinct seasons, bringing a feeling of relaxation and comfort. The land of kimchi also impresses with its massive architecture and diverse cultural and culinary space.</p>
            <p class="handbook-title-1 mt-3">Four seasons in Korea</p>
            <p class="handbook-content-1 mt-2">Korea has four distinct seasons. Spring is from March to May, the weather is warm. If you travel during this season, you will find your love for Korea doubled because the weather and nature are both very beautiful. This is an ideal time for outdoor activities, especially with many flower festivals held across the country.</p>
